{
    "title": "How to learn Next.Js",
    "content": "<h2 data-start=\"218\" data-end=\"277\">\u26A1 The Power of Next.js: Modern Web Development Made Easy<\/h2>\r\n<p data-start=\"279\" data-end=\"623\"><strong data-start=\"279\" data-end=\"290\">Next.js<\/strong> is not just another JavaScript framework \u2014 it\u2019s a complete toolkit for building high-performance, scalable web applications. Whether you're a React developer or just diving into modern frontend development, Next.js offers you the power of static site generation (SSG), server-side rendering (SSR), and much more, all in one package.<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"625\" data-end=\"653\">In this blog, we\u2019ll explore:<\/p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"655\" data-end=\"833\">\r\n    <li data-start=\"655\" data-end=\"673\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"657\" data-end=\"673\">What is Next.js?<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"674\" data-end=\"710\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"676\" data-end=\"710\">Key features that make it powerful<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"711\" data-end=\"745\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"713\" data-end=\"745\">How to create your first project<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"746\" data-end=\"778\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"748\" data-end=\"778\">Page routing and dynamic paths<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"779\" data-end=\"812\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"781\" data-end=\"812\">Static vs Server-side rendering<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"813\" data-end=\"833\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"815\" data-end=\"833\">Deployment options<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"815\" data-end=\"833\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"815\" data-end=\"833\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"835\" data-end=\"838\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"840\" data-end=\"863\">\uD83D\uDE80 What is Next.js?<\/h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"865\" data-end=\"1012\">Next.js is a <strong data-start=\"878\" data-end=\"903\">React-based framework<\/strong> created by <strong data-start=\"915\" data-end=\"925\">Vercel<\/strong> that helps developers build fast, SEO-friendly, and production-ready web applications.<\/p>\r\n<blockquote data-start=\"1014\" data-end=\"1153\">\r\n    <p data-start=\"1016\" data-end=\"1153\">\uD83D\uDCA1 It abstracts a lot of the boilerplate while giving you access to React, routing, rendering modes, and API routes \u2014 all out of the box.<\/p>\r\n<\/blockquote>\r\n<p data-start=\"1016\" data-end=\"1153\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1016\" data-end=\"1153\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"1155\" data-end=\"1158\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1160\" data-end=\"1179\">\uD83E\uDDF0 Key Features<\/h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"1181\" data-end=\"1216\">Here\u2019s why developers love Next.js:<\/p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1218\" data-end=\"1643\">\r\n    <li data-start=\"1218\" data-end=\"1300\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1220\" data-end=\"1300\">\uD83D\uDD04 <strong data-start=\"1223\" data-end=\"1245\">File-based routing<\/strong>: Pages are created by files in the <code data-start=\"1281\" data-end=\"1289\">pages\/<\/code> directory.<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"1301\" data-end=\"1382\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1303\" data-end=\"1382\">\u26A1 <strong data-start=\"1305\" data-end=\"1322\">Pre-rendering<\/strong>: Choose between Static Generation or Server-side Rendering.<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"1383\" data-end=\"1459\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1385\" data-end=\"1459\">\uD83E\uDDE0 <strong data-start=\"1388\" data-end=\"1402\">API routes<\/strong>: Create serverless functions easily in the same project.<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"1460\" data-end=\"1522\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1462\" data-end=\"1522\">\uD83D\uDCA8 <strong data-start=\"1465\" data-end=\"1496\">Built-in CSS &amp; Sass support<\/strong> (also Tailwind friendly).<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"1523\" data-end=\"1585\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1525\" data-end=\"1585\">\uD83C\uDF10 <strong data-start=\"1528\" data-end=\"1552\">Internationalization<\/strong>: Multi-language routing support.<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n    <li data-start=\"1586\" data-end=\"1643\">\r\n        <p data-start=\"1588\" data-end=\"1643\">\uD83D\uDD12 <strong data-start=\"1591\" data-end=\"1613\">Image optimization<\/strong>: Automatic with <code data-start=\"1630\" data-end=\"1642\">next\/image<\/code>.<\/p>\r\n    <\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"1588\" data-end=\"1643\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1588\" data-end=\"1643\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"1645\" data-end=\"1648\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1650\" data-end=\"1682\">\uD83D\uDEE0\uFE0F Setting Up a New Project<\/h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"1684\" data-end=\"1715\">Let\u2019s create a new Next.js app:<\/p>\r\n<div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\">\r\n    <div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]\">bash<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-bash\"><span>npx create-next-app@latest my-next-app\r\n            <\/span><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">cd<\/span><span> my-next-app\r\n                npm run dev\r\n            <\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<p data-start=\"1796\" data-end=\"1868\">Open <code data-start=\"1801\" data-end=\"1824\">http:\/\/localhost:3000<\/code> and you\u2019ll see the default landing page. \uD83C\uDF89<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1796\" data-end=\"1868\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1796\" data-end=\"1868\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"1870\" data-end=\"1873\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1875\" data-end=\"1899\">\uD83D\uDCC1 Project Structure<\/h3>\r\n<div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\">\r\n    <div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]\">arduino<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre!\"><span>my-next-app\/\r\n                \u251C\u2500\u2500 pages\/\r\n                \u2502 &nbsp; \u251C\u2500\u2500 index.js &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-comment\">\/\/ Home page<\/span><span>\r\n                \u2502 &nbsp; \u2514\u2500\u2500 about.js &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-comment\">\/\/ Another route<\/span><span>\r\n                \u251C\u2500\u2500 <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public<\/span><span>\/\r\n                \u251C\u2500\u2500 styles\/\r\n                \u251C\u2500\u2500 next.config.js\r\n                \u2514\u2500\u2500 package.json\r\n            <\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<p data-start=\"2074\" data-end=\"2114\">Create a new page just by adding a file:<\/p>\r\n<div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\">\r\n    <div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]\">jsx<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-jsx\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">\/\/ pages\/about.js<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">About<\/span><span>(<\/span><span class=\"hljs-params\"><\/span><span>) {\r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"language-xml hljs-tag\">&lt;<\/span><span class=\"language-xml hljs-tag hljs-name\">h1<\/span><span>&gt;About Us<\/span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;\/<\/span><span class=\"hljs-tag hljs-name\">h1<\/span><span>&gt;\r\n                }\r\n            <\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<p data-start=\"2209\" data-end=\"2268\">Now navigate to <code data-start=\"2225\" data-end=\"2233\">\/about<\/code> \u2014 no routing configuration needed.<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"2209\" data-end=\"2268\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"2209\" data-end=\"2268\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"2270\" data-end=\"2273\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"2275\" data-end=\"2297\">\uD83D\uDD01 Dynamic Routing<\/h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"2299\" data-end=\"2338\">Want dynamic paths like <code data-start=\"2323\" data-end=\"2337\">\/blog\/[slug]<\/code>?<\/p>\r\n<div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\">\r\n    <div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]\">jsx<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"sticky top-9\">\r\n        <div class=\"absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2\">\r\n            <div class=\"bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-jsx\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">\/\/ pages\/blog\/[slug].js<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import<\/span><span> { useRouter } <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-string\">'next\/router'<\/span><span>\r\n            \r\n            <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">BlogPost<\/span><span>(<\/span><span class=\"hljs-params\"><\/span><span>) {\r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const<\/span><span> router = <\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">useRouter<\/span><span>()\r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const<\/span><span> { slug } = router.<\/span><span class=\"hljs-property\">query<\/span><span>\r\n            \r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"language-xml hljs-tag\">&lt;<\/span><span class=\"language-xml hljs-tag hljs-name\">h1<\/span><span>&gt;Reading blog: {slug}<\/span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;\/<\/span><span class=\"hljs-tag hljs-name\">h1<\/span><span>&gt;\r\n                }\r\n            <\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<p data-start=\"2557\" data-end=\"2599\">Visit <code data-start=\"2563\" data-end=\"2583\">\/blog\/nextjs-intro<\/code> \u2014 and it works!<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"2557\" data-end=\"2599\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"2557\" data-end=\"2599\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"2601\" data-end=\"2604\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"2606\" data-end=\"2639\">\uD83E\uDDF1 Static vs Server Rendering<\/h3>\r\n<h4 data-start=\"2641\" data-end=\"2681\">Static Generation (faster, cached):<\/h4>\r\n<div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\">\r\n    <div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]\">js<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">async<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">getStaticProps<\/span><span>(<\/span><span class=\"hljs-params\"><\/span><span>) {\r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return<\/span><span> { <\/span><span class=\"hljs-attr\">props<\/span><span>: { <\/span><span class=\"hljs-attr\">name<\/span><span>: <\/span><span class=\"hljs-string\">'Static'<\/span><span> } }\r\n                }\r\n            <\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<h4 data-start=\"2776\" data-end=\"2829\">Server-side Rendering (dynamic on each request):<\/h4>\r\n<div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\">\r\n    <div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]\">js<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"sticky top-9\">\r\n        <div class=\"absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2\">\r\n            <div class=\"bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs\"><span data-state=\"closed\"><button class=\"flex gap-1 items-center select-none px-4 py-1\" aria-label=\"Copy\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"icon-xs\">\r\n                            <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path>\r\n                        <\/svg>Copy<\/button><button class=\"flex items-center gap-1 px-4 py-1 select-none\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"icon-xs\">\r\n                            <path d=\"M2.5 5.5C4.3 5.2 5.2 4 5.5 2.5C5.8 4 6.7 5.2 8.5 5.5C6.7 5.8 5.8 7 5.5 8.5C5.2 7 4.3 5.8 2.5 5.5Z\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><\/path>\r\n                            <path d=\"M5.66282 16.5231L5.18413 19.3952C5.12203 19.7678 5.09098 19.9541 5.14876 20.0888C5.19933 20.2067 5.29328 20.3007 5.41118 20.3512C5.54589 20.409 5.73218 20.378 6.10476 20.3159L8.97693 19.8372C9.72813 19.712 10.1037 19.6494 10.4542 19.521C10.7652 19.407 11.0608 19.2549 11.3343 19.068C11.6425 18.8575 11.9118 18.5882 12.4503 18.0497L20 10.5C21.3807 9.11929 21.3807 6.88071 20 5.5C18.6193 4.11929 16.3807 4.11929 15 5.5L7.45026 13.0497C6.91175 13.5882 6.6425 13.8575 6.43197 14.1657C6.24513 14.4392 6.09299 14.7348 5.97903 15.0458C5.85062 15.3963 5.78802 15.7719 5.66282 16.5231Z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><\/path>\r\n                            <path d=\"M14.5 7L18.5 11\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><\/path>\r\n                        <\/svg>Edit<\/button><\/span><\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">async<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">getServerSideProps<\/span><span>(<\/span><span class=\"hljs-params\"><\/span><span>) {\r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const<\/span><span> data = <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">await<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">fetch<\/span><span>(<\/span><span class=\"hljs-string\">'https:\/\/api.example.com\/data'<\/span><span>)\r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return<\/span><span> { <\/span><span class=\"hljs-attr\">props<\/span><span>: { data } }\r\n                }\r\n            <\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<p data-start=\"2977\" data-end=\"3040\">Use <code data-start=\"2981\" data-end=\"2999\">getStaticPaths()<\/code> with dynamic routes to pre-render pages.<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"2977\" data-end=\"3040\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<p data-start=\"2977\" data-end=\"3040\">&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n<hr data-start=\"3042\" data-end=\"3045\">\r\n<h3 data-start=\"3047\" data-end=\"3079\">\uD83C\uDFA8 Styling with Tailwind CSS<\/h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"3081\" data-end=\"3123\">Install and configure Tailwind in minutes:<\/p>\r\n<div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\">\r\n    <div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]\">bash<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-bash\"><span>npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer\r\n                npx tailwindcss init -p\r\n            <\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<p data-start=\"3210\" data-end=\"3278\">Update your <code data-start=\"3222\" data-end=\"3242\">tailwind.config.js<\/code> and import styles in <code data-start=\"3264\" data-end=\"3277\">globals.css<\/code>.<\/p>\r\n<div class=\"contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary\">\r\n    <div class=\"flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]\">jsx<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"sticky top-9\">\r\n        <div class=\"absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2\">\r\n            <div class=\"bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"whitespace-pre! language-jsx\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">\/\/ pages\/index.js<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">Home<\/span><span>(<\/span><span class=\"hljs-params\"><\/span><span>) {\r\n                &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return<\/span><span> (\r\n                &nbsp; &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"language-xml hljs-tag\">&lt;<\/span><span class=\"language-xml hljs-tag hljs-name\">div<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-attr\">className<\/span><span>=<\/span><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"flex justify-center items-center h-screen bg-gray-100\"<\/span><span>&gt;\r\n                &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-tag hljs-name\">h1<\/span><span> <\/span><span class=\"hljs-attr\">className<\/span><span>=<\/span><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600\"<\/span><span>&gt;Welcome to Next.js<\/span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;\/<\/span><span class=\"hljs-tag hljs-name\">h1<\/span><span>&gt;\r\n                &nbsp; &nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;\/<\/span><span class=\"hljs-tag hljs-name\">div<\/span><span>&gt;\r\n                &nbsp;)\r\n                }<\/span><\/code><\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"overflow-y-auto p-4\" dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"ove